[{"short_id":"2ng9uk","created_at":"2026-03-04T02:54:08.000-06:00","title":"RTL: WTF: Read the web like Right-to-Left readers do","url":"https://rtl.wtf/","score":1,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"kana","user_is_author":false,"tags":["a11y","web"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/2ng9uk","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/2ng9uk/rtl_wtf_read_web_like_right_left_readers_do"},{"short_id":"ya5b5h","created_at":"2026-03-04T02:24:51.000-06:00","title":"Meta: Add `Guix` tag","url":"","score":4,"flags":0,"comment_count":1,"description":"\u003cp\u003eIt is viewed as just a nix fork with scheme on top of in many communities I am in, while yes it might be started off as that but it has grown significantly in the recent years that it should be treated as its own project.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI have been just in guix community for like year and so but I have seen very good changes, some of them would\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eThe new rust build system\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoving to Codeberg (this brought many new contributors)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003enew v1.5.0 release :)\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut what I like most about the guix project is the people there, It is small but very tightly-knit community. So I believe guix deserve its own tag now.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"It is viewed as just a nix fork with scheme on top of in many communities I am in, while yes it might be started off as that but it has grown significantly in the recent years that it should be treated as its own project.\r\n\r\nI have been just in guix community for like year and so but I have seen very good changes, some of them would\r\n\r\n- The new rust build system\r\n- Moving to Codeberg (this brought many new contributors)\r\n- new v1.5.0 release :)\r\n\r\nBut what I like most about the guix project is the people there, It is small but very tightly-knit community. So I bel